%md
# Overview
## About raw data
* 기상청 UV 데이터 (시간단위)
* source : 직접문의 (기상자료개방포털은 일단위만 올라옴)
* fname format (hdfs) : /raw/kma_aws/locode_UV(A,B)_yyyymmdd_L1.txt
* content format
    > Site: Gosan
    yyyymmddhh,  sum_UVA[MJ/m2],  max_UVA[W/m2]
    2017010100,    0.0000,    0.0000
    2017010101,    0.0000,    0.0000
    2017010102,    0.0000,    0.0000


## About formatted data
* raw data -> parquet dataframe으로 변환 (dh, sum_uva, max_uva, sum_uvb, max_uvb)
* dh(datahour) : "yyyy-mm-dd hh"
* sum_uva
    - 단위 : MJ/m2
    - 
* max_uva
    - 단위 : W/m2
    - 
* sum_uvb
    - 단위 : KJ/m2
    - 
* max_uvb
    - 단위 : W/m2
    -

msg.data:
Overview

About raw data

  • 기상청 UV 데이터 (시간단위)
  • source : 직접문의 (기상자료개방포털은 일단위만 올라옴)
  • fname format (hdfs) : /raw/kma_aws/locode_UV(A,B)_yyyymmdd_L1.txt

  • content format

    Site: Gosan
    yyyymmddhh, sum_UVA[MJ/m2], max_UVA[W/m2]
    2017010100, 0.0000, 0.0000
    2017010101, 0.0000, 0.0000
    2017010102, 0.0000, 0.0000

About formatted data

  • raw data -> parquet dataframe으로 변환 (dh, sum_uva, max_uva, sum_uvb, max_uvb)
  • dh(datahour) : “yyyy-mm-dd hh”
  • sum_uva
    • 단위 : MJ/m2
  • max_uva
    • 단위 : W/m2
  • sum_uvb
    • 단위 : KJ/m2
  • max_uvb
    • 단위 : W/m2
      -

paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
from pyspark.sql import Row

uva = sc.textFile('hdfs:///raw/kma_uva_2017')\
        .filter(lambda s: s != 'Site: Anmyeon')\
        .map(lambda s: s.split(','))\
        .filter(lambda s: is_number(s[1].strip()))\
        .map(lambda s: [s[0][:4] + '-' + s[0][4:6] + '-' + s[0][6:8],
                        s[0][8:],
                        float(s[1].strip()),
                        float(s[2].strip())])\
        .map(lambda s: Row(datehour=s[0]+ ' ' + s[1], sum_uva=s[2], max_uva=s[3]))\
        .toDF()

uvb = sc.textFile('hdfs:///raw/kma_uvb_2017')\
        .filter(lambda s: s != 'Site: Anmyeon')\
        .map(lambda s: s.split(','))\
        .filter(lambda s: is_number(s[1].strip()))\
        .map(lambda s: [s[0][:4] + '-' + s[0][4:6] + '-' + s[0][6:8],
                        s[0][8:],
                        float(s[1].strip()),
                        float(s[2].strip())])\
        .map(lambda s: Row(datehour=s[0]+ ' ' + s[1], sum_uvb=s[2], max_uvb=s[3]))\
        .toDF()
